{% extends 'base.html' %}
{% load staticfiles %}

{% block title %}
   {{page_title}}
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<h2>{{view_title}}</h2>
<p>Thank you for submitting your application to {{sub_verb}} at the Great Burlesque Exposition.
Your application will go to our panel of reviewers as soon as your submission fee has been paid. </p>

<p>Ahem.</p>

<p>Yes, about that. There is just one more detail to attend to. A small matter of the fee. 
If you follow the link below, you'll be discreetly whisked away to the Brown Paper Tickets site to pay your application fee. 

<p>Some more blather here.</p>

   <form action="/bpt_handoff" method="post">
   {% csrf_token %}
   <input type='hidden' name='bid_type' value='{{bid_type}}'>
   <input type='hidden' name='bid_id' value='{{bid.pk}}'>
   <input type='hidden' name='user_id' value='{{user.pk}}'>
   <input type="submit" name="draft" value="Take me to BPT to pay!">
   </form>


<p>Once you pay your application fee, your application details will be locked so the reviewers can review. </p>


<p>Your token is {{token}}</p>
<p>Your tokenstring is {{token_string}}</p>

{% endblock %}
